{"tid":422551,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(行路撚)冰島行山(多圖少字)","createTime":"2017-10-03T06:54:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T17:38:13.000Z","uid":110155,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"fb1f5e974053bd782472a9a6dd2be97c4581c6f7","tid":422551,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:54:11.000Z","msg":"今年中去歐洲行山，之前係連登出過一個「法國意大利瑞士行山」，更新完之後因為太忙，就無繼續寫冰島個部分，宜家補返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/328371/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/328371/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n冰島，對我這個從未踏足過歐洲的人來說，是何其遙遠，聽說她物價全球超貴，聽說她天氣變幻莫測，她很貼引，但一直都不在我的旅遊計劃之內。<br />\n<br />\n直至我認識了Laugavegur Trail，這條全球二十大徒步路線，令我決定踏足這個冰與火的國度。2017年6月14日，我剛在法國完成十天的環白朗峰步道Tour du Mont Blanc後，我終於向冰島進發。為了省錢，我在法國買了7天的食物，打算在冰島時「食自己」，交通以順風車為主，以帳篷為家，自給自足，減少在冰島的開銷。<br />\n<br />\n當我離開冰島國際機場，旅客們向巴士站前進，我卻以步行的方式，走到機場道路上第一個分叉路口，打算在那裡截順風車。雖然出發前已經知道在冰島截順風車不難，但總是心大心細，加上天開始下雨，令我開始擔心，自己是不是做了一個錯誤的決定。幸好在十五分鐘後，已經有好心的冰島人，載我到首都雷克雅未克。來到首都的我，第一時間找到書店，購買有關Laugavegur Trail的登山指南後，我就開始走路到首都郊區，打算隨便找個地方露營，第二天早上再出發到公路口截風車。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/Y9Xel9onS2s80l_kTw2a6A1Lpuv1r6RaC3BWJ2yinQaSRA_yoheOt_h7iY51J175jcFBKjFWcLrG1eHiAB0KRQcOkg=s0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FY9Xel9onS2s80l_kTw2a6A1Lpuv1r6RaC3BWJ2yinQaSRA_yoheOt_h7iY51J175jcFBKjFWcLrG1eHiAB0KRQcOkg%3Ds0&h=3cf397e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/vQAMfFuIo7ZUcJJiCnOGaq4jtSyZX6pJOqLev8FE87DtGuZcv-eQSFxa4hr5PewUqyhLl07tXLK9F-Zf4ZSSaCU=s0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FvQAMfFuIo7ZUcJJiCnOGaq4jtSyZX6pJOqLev8FE87DtGuZcv-eQSFxa4hr5PewUqyhLl07tXLK9F-Zf4ZSSaCU%3Ds0&h=d171160d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二天早上，我收拾好東西，開始往Laugavegur Trail的起點Landmannalaugar出發，不過老實說，這次順風車行程難度不低，因為Landmannalaugar是冰島知名旅遊景點，除了旅客外本地人不多，自駕的話一定要開四驅車才可以進去，所以一般旅客也是坐巴士進去，路上車量不多。雖然我很順利截到幾輛順風車，但路程也不遠，直至一對來自駕遊的比利時夫婦願意載我一程，我才成功來到Landmannalaugar。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/0fDvsSUPx6NsdgTmgblopUzJ81adI1vEvjDooxqcxIJVkLgv7DUbIwi9RVtsDx52SeJC602jacJI-ViNXLvsbq8K=s0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2F0fDvsSUPx6NsdgTmgblopUzJ81adI1vEvjDooxqcxIJVkLgv7DUbIwi9RVtsDx52SeJC602jacJI-ViNXLvsbq8K%3Ds0&h=22173d9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/A_9dx_ZEZ_rzJcMo6Lm7n2Ugc-ucDmqJRr7UX4U4pwIorYEzvmm9upmMEyXt_36pFO2CoUH_2J1B7sdYP1AUnrx1YA=s0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FA_9dx_ZEZ_rzJcMo6Lm7n2Ugc-ucDmqJRr7UX4U4pwIorYEzvmm9upmMEyXt_36pFO2CoUH_2J1B7sdYP1AUnrx1YA%3Ds0&h=aa786923&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"026d855d56d2b7fdf3a2c4c5026712a489171b35","tid":422551,"uid":110155,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:55:16.000Z","msg":"當我在來這裡的路上時，有冰島司機對我說，Landmannalaugar是全冰島最漂亮的地區，其至說她是全世界最美也不為過，雖然他的話可能有誇張成分，但也令我期待不已。當我開始走Laugavegur Trail，才知道他所言非虛。去年我選擇走美國太平洋屋脊步道，其中一個原因是它的多樣性，走在這超過四千公里的長度，在四個半月裡穿越沙漠，雪山，森林，火山等多種地貌，而這次Laugavegur Trail也有類似的情況，不過只有55公里的她，已經能夠令我感受到這種變化！我由Landmannalaugar起步，第一天是以彩色火山為主，不同的礦物，令地表和山丘出現不同的顏色，再加上白雪舖在山上，更添美感，多個位置更會噴出熱氣，空氣中瀰漫着礦物的氣味，令這個區域看起來像異域一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/oBNnVDR1I6axZYC2qDChWNrMSiMIkILULR2yq9ubWWyxysrMDZaMVYfc8cJmBgCvD_HwbDOXfm103vA8dwgWW8X6=s0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FoBNnVDR1I6axZYC2qDChWNrMSiMIkILULR2yq9ubWWyxysrMDZaMVYfc8cJmBgCvD_HwbDOXfm103vA8dwgWW8X6%3Ds0&h=f65bddce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gkzvWBHvMcg_GwtsEVy8McdE0KTgWIQqKcmaFJ_4NenxcXJXyL7vsLrpMnm1fsRAB9QwOm8b-N63p13e5hnC65iydA=s0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FgkzvWBHvMcg_GwtsEVy8McdE0KTgWIQqKcmaFJ_4NenxcXJXyL7vsLrpMnm1fsRAB9QwOm8b-N63p13e5hnC65iydA%3Ds0&h=89172914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/DM0Z_sV-cRLSxYcll2GbYt3lhwHVyT-U40I6obWUe4g-HQgO4Nx2b-cJGchhTJfO6pUbkaGNIeckDYiM-XTX3X4=s0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FDM0Z_sV-cRLSxYcll2GbYt3lhwHVyT-U40I6obWUe4g-HQgO4Nx2b-cJGchhTJfO6pUbkaGNIeckDYiM-XTX3X4%3Ds0&h=6c6c25ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/5HodmGCfLGTuLGrx5_8a719lMGsSg6LRAfyxxgR_GIIGUNKLeTZFFEBkZz01lNdmNiEbEwALlZalpzGTF7_V2QfUnQ=s0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2F5HodmGCfLGTuLGrx5_8a719lMGsSg6LRAfyxxgR_GIIGUNKLeTZFFEBkZz01lNdmNiEbEwALlZalpzGTF7_V2QfUnQ%3Ds0&h=0144e709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/T_MU2a9CBUSIMQ87J9WhfvV7hv94JWYBcFyIjSU6u2yqkYQocnm-ok5h1BL9Nqo129wXsrN4P9NWxFsyEK7DOV4=s0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FT_MU2a9CBUSIMQ87J9WhfvV7hv94JWYBcFyIjSU6u2yqkYQocnm-ok5h1BL9Nqo129wXsrN4P9NWxFsyEK7DOV4%3Ds0&h=17fa08d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e79396aa7576c261c91dbf0dd22bd6bf69f954f9","tid":422551,"uid":24682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84496894b152eb5ee599b0d0fff0f5c9658e0fd","tid":422551,"uid":135790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:01:51.000Z","msg":"好嘢係要留個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5df081e7b4d9e7edac1c046f558e56c8a4c1c13","tid":422551,"uid":24682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:01:57.000Z","msg":"之前追哂巴打美國PCT個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6162a7ae86d97a45ea8bd6c98b58ea5cb75b6214","tid":422551,"uid":110155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:02:01.000Z","msg":"當高度開始爬升，雪也愈來愈多，環境又變成了一片雪原，走在看不見盡頭的雪上，辛苦累人，但也是另一種完全不同的體驗。就只是第一天，就已經有兩種已經不一樣的體驗！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/KqspE5hc9yYh8Zkos2uSUDnyrobJurG8Goqd_9K44XTFfbXCqh6-8RgeQ3A63NVMRGrcrHizoQc6gkZeJSGMR7GnjA=s0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FKqspE5hc9yYh8Zkos2uSUDnyrobJurG8Goqd_9K44XTFfbXCqh6-8RgeQ3A63NVMRGrcrHizoQc6gkZeJSGMR7GnjA%3Ds0&h=43bc2fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/KdUK_kdJlRM0XSyJQjT4WAvpaYjM-ve5qnR5rKtRrdGEiMXPUpCcec6QeuHyZAJLkwoV60yS4l7fntNqs4RC7Kk=s0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FKdUK_kdJlRM0XSyJQjT4WAvpaYjM-ve5qnR5rKtRrdGEiMXPUpCcec6QeuHyZAJLkwoV60yS4l7fntNqs4RC7Kk%3Ds0&h=d4194d23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/145755_a7adcce0a4eb2e2c22c03a85e9aa4e68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F145755_a7adcce0a4eb2e2c22c03a85e9aa4e68.jpg&h=d6b5ec43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/145831_a6686dab89510d8f018a2a770abad4ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F145831_a6686dab89510d8f018a2a770abad4ba.jpg&h=aab2f783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/145913_0e163f57386dea98492cb5b8e62768d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F145913_0e163f57386dea98492cb5b8e62768d3.jpg&h=23d24fd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/150004_7726eadf0e9bc96dac242b6d763e8ae6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F150004_7726eadf0e9bc96dac242b6d763e8ae6.jpg&h=ccd4cb46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/150037_14663d0b03319077d529eec542e84c28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F150037_14663d0b03319077d529eec542e84c28.jpg&h=2ce000fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/150117_bc85bee06a0ea3d0a65830714bd4705f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F150117_bc85bee06a0ea3d0a65830714bd4705f.jpg&h=15242c32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2609d2df4530ff2ba0a3f4152f86a1c18d40739a","tid":422551,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:02:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前追哂巴打美國PCT個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3683e1358996edce3a110b5cc6f460979566f4d","tid":422551,"uid":141590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:21:57.000Z","msg":"大師兄返嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留個靚名先"},{"pid":"5f8d68a10b58da8a859de560d21a90d974b68a08","tid":422551,"uid":41089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:30:20.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645eeb018489a1a36f58051e63eb8f9eb09d27f9","tid":422551,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:31:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大師兄返嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留個靚名先</blockquote><br />\n其實冰島依次好短，好快就upload完<br />\n<br />\n黎緊10月7日去日本行山"},{"pid":"69eb34f346e659c7243a224bf945a3cc33e23b7d","tid":422551,"uid":24759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:39:35.000Z","msg":"勇者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6211c76f8fbb738c05052bd984da0f6276386cd3","tid":422551,"uid":59544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:46:26.000Z","msg":"adore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d29eb872c84e884cca6d01862daf88990aa09ee9","tid":422551,"uid":71175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3767c0fa1ab50c25984bfc7fe7011bc7ce8a7ce6","tid":422551,"uid":29295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:51:59.000Z","msg":"正皮咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c0394e4eb5a7c8833a1742b4804dc225b62d2b","tid":422551,"uid":126707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d4c6bd638fece9ca4cc0d5e4312d9ae0a7301c","tid":422551,"uid":50408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:01:36.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26998cec53037565a6c18d9169071cf9dae306df","tid":422551,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:03:25.000Z","msg":"留名！！"},{"pid":"f6b0ff7838816fc69a370cb840a73e8a9f08571a","tid":422551,"uid":11271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:34:41.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2d0466aa938bb0b49a9f94f82a282e098a042c","tid":422551,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T10:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/183458_b87396d46f7836a5c4691206217f0b7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F183458_b87396d46f7836a5c4691206217f0b7a.jpg&h=9d56abca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一間山屋，但有得睇無得住，因為我係窮L，住一晚要80美金....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/JaVruk555RRYV3N4wb6d5xtuPH-M_DPkIVBnPZ-EUNtfM6S8BySytSLOOHVjl5YaOV5JqBKCIzoQ_2cE_-ik2bjDYA=s0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FJaVruk555RRYV3N4wb6d5xtuPH-M_DPkIVBnPZ-EUNtfM6S8BySytSLOOHVjl5YaOV5JqBKCIzoQ_2cE_-ik2bjDYA%3Ds0&h=9ef30c52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n窮L只可以露營<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/183724_51d96ea8efe3b816b1bd18908aa460b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F183724_51d96ea8efe3b816b1bd18908aa460b4.jpg&h=367a6482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同場見到有商業登山團，可以開車幫你送行李，仲煮野幫你食....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/183847_a2617e76a6af4b64e1b1cd2ddf59c882.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F183847_a2617e76a6af4b64e1b1cd2ddf59c882.jpg&h=a2b7df2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彩色石頭"},{"pid":"f40750d772ab9cbfadbf6b47712d1470170c4f3d","tid":422551,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T10:41:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bf200fb2813f5d897a9d7e831b3ecd8b6ad863f","tid":422551,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T10:47:51.000Z","msg":"來到第二日，當我離開雪原地帶，卻又來到了綠色星球，不過細心一看，綠中帶黑，原來這些山丘都是黑色的泥土組成，綠色的不是雜草，而是青苔，當我踩在青苔之上時，已經感到它的彈性，在我把腳放開後，被踩的部分卻會回復原狀，可見青苔之厚，足以承托我的重量，用手摸着，感覺並不噁心，而是一種像羊毛地毯的觸感，非常舒服。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/fz7wKAI0Kx_9ZVrVoByMYoCMUz9WAXZHj2kude-aPRew7Otvl5rquzHcJOli_uCdL8w8bP4z1Ps1b-YJWqZhg9k=s0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Ffz7wKAI0Kx_9ZVrVoByMYoCMUz9WAXZHj2kude-aPRew7Otvl5rquzHcJOli_uCdL8w8bP4z1Ps1b-YJWqZhg9k%3Ds0&h=7f018a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LeNofE2S_jMPJMruLRTDrL5y_ErE4wLc_1LoJClB5wCZjqjcZqtr3LJRgbOIXhgntUXV2MCHMndtEkhkXga5Tsk=s0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FLeNofE2S_jMPJMruLRTDrL5y_ErE4wLc_1LoJClB5wCZjqjcZqtr3LJRgbOIXhgntUXV2MCHMndtEkhkXga5Tsk%3Ds0&h=2902628e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/ZAdmq0Qb5aOHwLYBAkiyhFVhnrbt2jZm8kamiN0AwiL1sLpAyEIWaTUhn2lg-a8ACxbmfT6i39z7s7Wct7w5a6F9=s0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FZAdmq0Qb5aOHwLYBAkiyhFVhnrbt2jZm8kamiN0AwiL1sLpAyEIWaTUhn2lg-a8ACxbmfT6i39z7s7Wct7w5a6F9%3Ds0&h=ac895879&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/4JHv3sa9JEUXg4J3j_IOvcUgJmfrxCugJCLQhOpx4FJ48DnSqx1mH2DpNKiOSCefRpZXvL5x8UFFSurZCA-99Die=s0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2F4JHv3sa9JEUXg4J3j_IOvcUgJmfrxCugJCLQhOpx4FJ48DnSqx1mH2DpNKiOSCefRpZXvL5x8UFFSurZCA-99Die%3Ds0&h=f3d1fe38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/184126_46dcd3f457c412d0aaef1bf1c1edab20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F184126_46dcd3f457c412d0aaef1bf1c1edab20.jpg&h=9d0455a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/184155_9b76aab11934d2dadf74069ea45c3451.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F184155_9b76aab11934d2dadf74069ea45c3451.jpg&h=e0d13887&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落左成日雨，忍唔住住山屋，依80美金，成為我係冰島最大一筆開支....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/184310_4c0487e826cfbf1c7893533d529f2c88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F184310_4c0487e826cfbf1c7893533d529f2c88.jpg&h=7061ef06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n終於可以唔洗擔心落雨嘅問題....<br />\n<br />\n因為我已經定左由冰島返香港嘅機票，所以就算我行快啲，返到首都都係無野做，仲要洗多啲錢，所以我決定行慢啲，願寧係山入面無得洗錢好過....<br />\n<br />\n由於我係只前個商業登山團遇到香港人，我就決定同佢地一齊行，一日由山屋到山屋，其實得十幾公里，而且難度好低，四五個鐘就得完，而商業登山隊當然無預多啲時間，所以會早少少出發，所以我每日都會係早上十一點先慢慢起身起步，再中途追返佢地....."},{"pid":"1416701df7c12bb48fbee52f0143d623d815399a","tid":422551,"uid":4568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:28:41.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40395e319d261362fe8d2bcfd22acdf68afa460b","tid":422551,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:30:30.000Z","msg":"推，好靚阿啲景"},{"pid":"5f706ca39a72fb3fe2099ca6e105f99584f4b250","tid":422551,"uid":56817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a168841ea5f2024d5866bcd4b778b15c2d134e","tid":422551,"uid":135730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:54:19.000Z","msg":"之前去過一次冰島 覺得唔算好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}